<%- include("partials/header") %>
    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6 text-white">
            About Us
        </h1>
        <hr class="mb-6 border-t-2 border-gray-700">

        <div class=" text-zinc-900 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg glass border border-zinc-700">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4 m-auto">Our Real Estate Management System</h2>
            <p class="mb-4 text-lg">
                Welcome to our Real Estate Management System! Our platform is designed to streamline the real estate
                process, making it easier for users to manage properties and appointments efficiently. Below are the
                core features and functionalities of our system:
            </p>

            <div class="mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">User Roles and Functionalities</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Agent:</strong> Can create properties and manage appointments.</li>
                    <li><strong>Buyer:</strong> Can book appointments to view properties.</li>
                    <li><strong>Seller:</strong> Can create properties and manage appointments.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Key Features</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-6 space-y-2">
                    <li><strong>Registration and Login:</strong> Users can register, log in, and manage their accounts.
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Password Management:</strong> Includes features for forgetting and resetting passwords.
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Property Creation:</strong> Agents and sellers can create new properties.</li>
                    <li><strong>Appointment Booking:</strong> Buyers can book appointments to view properties.</li>
                    <li><strong>Property Listings:</strong> The homepage displays all created properties.</li>
                    <li><strong>Profile Management:</strong> Users can view and manage their property details,
                        appointment details, and personal information on their profile page.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">How It Works</h3>
                <p class="text-lg mb-4">
                    On the homepage, users can view a list of all created properties. Buyers can book appointments for
                    properties they are interested in. Agents and sellers can create new properties to be listed on the
                    site. Each user role has specific functionalities and permissions to ensure a smooth and efficient
                    process.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg">
                    The profile page serves as a central hub where users can see detailed information about their
                    properties, appointments, and personal details. Users can also perform actions like creating
                    properties or booking appointments based on their role.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
